<div class="main-grid">

    <div class="clear-box"></div>

    <div class="header col-100">
        <div class="header-text">
            <h1>CoffeeWork</h1>
            <h2>THE COWORKING NETWORK</h2>
            <p class='header-paragraph'>Connect with the makers, the entrepreneurs, and the designers of co-working spaces.
                Take a look at what the members of your co-working space are up to and grab coffee with them. Not a member yet? That's okay!
                <br>
                Join a new co-working space and be a part of the community.
             </p>
        <div style="border:5px; border-style:solid; border-color:white; padding: 3em;" class="border-box">
             <p style= "font-size: 30px;">The Farm</p>
             <button class="signup-button">
                <p class="signup">
                    <%= link_to 'Join', signup_path %>
                </p>
            </button>
            <button class="signup-button">
               <p class="signup">
                   <%= link_to 'View Members', signup_path %>
               </p>
           </button>
         </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="clear-box"></div>

    <div class="students">
        <div class="student col-66">
            <h2 class="exploration-header">STUDENT EXPLORATION</h2>
            <div class="line-separator"></div>
            <p class="exploration-text">The number of career opportunities for college students
            is almost endless. CoffeeAlum makes exploring those
            avenues easier by connecting students with alumni.</p>
        </div>
        <div id="tester" class="student col-33">
            <div class="coffee"></div>
            <div class="student-quote">
                <div class="quote-block">
                    <p class="quote-text">Choosing a career is hard. Coffee isn't.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="clear-box"></div>

    <div class="alumni">
        <div class="alumni col-66">
            <h2 class="alumni-header">ALUMNI WISDOM</h2>
            <div class="alumni-line-separator"></div>
            <p class="alumni-text">Take part in the construction of a vibrant community
            of students and alumni. At your own convenience, you can talk with undergraduates
            that can probably learn a thing or two from you.</p>
        </div>

        <div id="test" class="alumni col-33">
            <div class="alumni-quote">
                <div class="alumni-quote-block">
                    <p class="alumni-quote-text"><q>Mentoring is a brain to pick, an ear
                    to listen and a push in the right direction</q></p>
                    <div class="holder">
                        <div class="author-line-separator"></div>
                        <h2 class="author">John C. Crosby</h2>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

    </div>
</div>
